  <brief_title>Randomized Controlled Trial of a Community Health Worker Program on Hearing Loss (Oyendo Bien)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Oyendo Bien: Reducing Disparities in Access to Hearing Health Care on the U.S.-Mexico Border</official_title>
